ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Atlantic Fisheries Regulations, 1985 and the Maritime Provinces Fishery Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending certain REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE FISHERIES ACT in order to maintain the application of existing departmental policies and introduce new licensing eligibility criteria and prohibitions respecting the use and control of the rights and privileges conferred under a licence to fish in the inshore and coastal fishing sector in Atlantic Canada and Quebec, where these regulations apply.
